tigernotes
==========================
Gao Wang (*) 2012, GNU GPL

Dependencies
------------
sudo apt-get install texlive texlive-xetex texlive-latex-extra texlive-fonts-extra texlive-extra-utils texlive-font-utils latex-beamer pgf latexmk latex-xcolor texlive-pstricks python-pygments 

Installation
------------
cd path/to/some/folder
svn co svn+ssh://usrname@csg.bcmd.bcm.edu/nfs/usr/local/svn/tigernotes ./
svn up
sudo python3 setup.py install

Help
----
tigernotes -h

DOC Example
-----------
tigernotes doc -h
tigernotes doc demo.notes --author "John Doe" --title "Example log documentation" -f --lite --output d1.pdf
tigernotes doc demo.notes --author "John Doe" --title "Example log documentation" --toc --output d2.pdf
tigernotes doc demo.notes --no_page_number --no_section_number --output d3.pdf

SLIDES Example
--------------
tigernotes slides -h
tigernotes slides demo.snotes -o d3
tigernotes slides demo.snotes --theme plain -o d4
tigernotes slides demo.snotes -a "John Doe" -t "Example log slides" -i "McDonald's" --toc -o d5
tigernotes slides demo.snotes -a "John Doe" -t "Example log slides" -i "McDonald's" --toc --theme heavy -o d6
tigernotes slides demo.snotes -a "John Doe" -t "Example log slides" --toc --mode handout -o d7
tigernotes slides demo.snotes -a "John Doe" -t "Example log slides" --toc --mode notes -o d8

HTML Example
------------
tigernotes html -h
tigernotes html demo.notes -o d1 --author "John Doe" --title "Example log documentation" --lite
tigernotes html demo.notes -o d2 --author "John Doe" --title "Example log documentation" --lite --columns 2
tigernotes html demo.notes -o d3 --author "John Doe" --title "Example log documentation" --toc --separate
tigernotes admin *.html -o index -a index_html 

DOKUWIKI Example
----------------
tigernotes dokuwiki -h
tigernotes dokuwiki demo.notes -o ~/html/data/pages/demo.txt --toc 

Syntax
------
###  ###				#{ ----------	#{out	#{table	#{ xxx (xxx = warning, important, tip, note)	#{list		#{ xxx (xxx = latex, bash, r, cpp, python, sql, php, text)
#!   #									#						#(or ##)
###, ###, #!, #!!, #!!!, #, #*, 	#} ----------,  #}	#}	#}     						#} 		#}

Emphasis: ``double quote'', `single quote',  "italics", ""bold"", """bold italics""", @@@raw \LaTeXe syntax@@@, @@monospaced@@, @url@, [keyword|footnote]

Known Issues
------------
html: cannot incorporate raw html codes in block or cmd mode (will conflict with the source)
